					<Card title="2. Mobile Development" description="Create beautifull mobile native apps as your expectation. Give me your design and workflow and rock it!"/>
					<Card title="3. Cloud Computing" description="Have a virtual server windows/linux but doesn't know how to use it? let's talk and serve your server"/>
					<Card title="4. Other" description="I dont know why you contact me if there is no reason and no problem you can contact me anytime haha :)"/>
				</div>
