					<img src="me.jpg" style="height: 300px" class="w-full"/>
					<div class="blog-details mt-3">
						<div class="flex mb-3 items-center gap-2">
							<div class="bg-green-500 text-white text-sm p-1 rounded-sm">Technology</div>
							<h5 class="text-sm">• 4min</h5>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-3xl mb-3 font-semibold">M1.00001 19C0.600015 12.6 21.5 11.3334 32 11.5C135.833?</h3>
						<h5 class="text-lg mb-3">Have a virtual server windows/linux but doesn't know how to use it? let's talk and serve your server</h5>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
