						<h5 class="text-lg text-slate-300 my-3">Why waiting so long ? Talk to me about your project and make it real now!</h5>
						<h5 class="text-lg text-green-500 fonr-medium">Let's Connect</h5>
					</div>
					<div class="basis-full md:basis-1/2">
						<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row flex-basis items-center gap-2 mb-2">
							<div class="basis-full md:basis-1/2 w-full">
								<input type="text" placeholder="Name" class="w-full py-4 px-5 bg-slate-300">
							</div>
							<div class="basis-full md:basis-1/2 w-full">
